{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1436,"text":"One hot October morning,"},{"time":4667,"text":"I got off the all-night train"},{"time":7401,"text":"in Mandalay,"},{"time":8583,"text":"the old royal capital of Burma,"},{"time":11725,"text":"now Myanmar."},{"time":13660,"text":"And out on the street, I ran into\na group of rough men"},{"time":17882,"text":"standing beside their bicycle rickshaws."},{"time":21799,"text":"And one of them came up"},{"time":23193,"text":"and offered to show me around."},{"time":26615,"text":"The price he quoted was outrageous."},{"time":29832,"text":"It was less than I would pay\nfor a bar of chocolate at home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33844,"text":"So I clambered into his trishaw,"},{"time":37009,"text":"and he began pedaling us slowly\nbetween palaces and pagodas."},{"time":43972,"text":"And as he did, he told me how\nhe had come to the city from his village."},{"time":49295,"text":"He'd earned a degree in mathematics."},{"time":51698,"text":"His dream was to be a teacher."},{"time":54445,"text":"But of course, life is hard\nunder a military dictatorship,"},{"time":59281,"text":"and so for now, this was the only way\nhe could make a living."},{"time":64796,"text":"Many nights, he told me,\nhe actually slept in his trishaw"},{"time":68761,"text":"so he could catch the first visitors\noff the all-night train."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75543,"text":"And very soon, we found\nthat in certain ways,"},{"time":79416,"text":"we had so much in common --"},{"time":81106,"text":"we were both in our 20s,"},{"time":82991,"text":"we were both fascinated\nby foreign cultures --"},{"time":86734,"text":"that he invited me home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90056,"text":"So we turned off the wide,\ncrowded streets,"},{"time":93887,"text":"and we began bumping\ndown rough, wild alleyways."},{"time":98121,"text":"There were broken shacks all around."},{"time":100493,"text":"I really lost the sense of where I was,"},{"time":104136,"text":"and I realized that anything\ncould happen to me now."},{"time":107842,"text":"I could get mugged or drugged"},{"time":110308,"text":"or something worse."},{"time":111648,"text":"Nobody would know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114309,"text":"Finally, he stopped and led me into a hut,"},{"time":118030,"text":"which consisted of just one tiny room."},{"time":122228,"text":"And then he leaned down,"},{"time":124429,"text":"and reached under his bed."},{"time":127608,"text":"And something in me froze."},{"time":132046,"text":"I waited to see what he would pull out."},{"time":135361,"text":"And finally he extracted a box."},{"time":139295,"text":"Inside it was every single letter\nhe had ever received"},{"time":144250,"text":"from visitors from abroad,"},{"time":147001,"text":"and on some of them he had pasted"},{"time":149127,"text":"little black-and-white worn snapshots"},{"time":152542,"text":"of his new foreign friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156387,"text":"So when we said goodbye that night,"},{"time":160038,"text":"I realized he had also shown me"},{"time":162649,"text":"the secret point of travel,"},{"time":164983,"text":"which is to take a plunge,"},{"time":167063,"text":"to go inwardly as well as outwardly"},{"time":169779,"text":"to places you would never go otherwise,"},{"time":172990,"text":"to venture into uncertainty,"},{"time":175928,"text":"ambiguity,"},{"time":177498,"text":"even fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180298,"text":"At home, it's dangerously easy"},{"time":182761,"text":"to assume we're on top of things."},{"time":185810,"text":"Out in the world, you are reminded\nevery moment that you're not,"},{"time":190309,"text":"and you can't get to the bottom\nof things, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194235,"text":"Everywhere, \"People wish to be settled,\""},{"time":197161,"text":"Ralph Waldo Emerson reminded us,"},{"time":199464,"text":"\"but only insofar\nas we are unsettled"},{"time":202164,"text":"is there any hope for us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":204891,"text":"At this conference,\nwe've been lucky enough"},{"time":207342,"text":"to hear some exhilarating\nnew ideas and discoveries"},{"time":210819,"text":"and, really, about all the ways"},{"time":212599,"text":"in which knowledge is being\npushed excitingly forwards."},{"time":216797,"text":"But at some point, knowledge gives out."},{"time":220802,"text":"And that is the moment"},{"time":222050,"text":"when your life is truly decided:"},{"time":225825,"text":"you fall in love;"},{"time":228093,"text":"you lose a friend;"},{"time":230893,"text":"the lights go out."},{"time":233000,"text":"And it's then, when you're lost\nor uneasy or carried out of yourself,"},{"time":238038,"text":"that you find out who you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242224,"text":"I don't believe that ignorance is bliss."},{"time":246193,"text":"Science has unquestionably made our lives"},{"time":249348,"text":"brighter and longer and healthier."},{"time":252825,"text":"And I am forever grateful to the teachers\nwho showed me the laws of physics"},{"time":257676,"text":"and pointed out that\nthree times three makes nine."},{"time":261678,"text":"I can count that out on my fingers"},{"time":264527,"text":"any time of night or day."},{"time":268802,"text":"But when a mathematician tells me"},{"time":270438,"text":"that minus three times\nminus three makes nine,"},{"time":273985,"text":"that's a kind of logic\nthat almost feels like trust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280674,"text":"The opposite of knowledge, in other words,\nisn't always ignorance."},{"time":284948,"text":"It can be wonder."},{"time":286482,"text":"Or mystery."},{"time":287964,"text":"Possibility."},{"time":289894,"text":"And in my life, I've found\nit's the things I don't know"},{"time":293755,"text":"that have lifted me up\nand pushed me forwards"},{"time":296458,"text":"much more than the things I do know."},{"time":300222,"text":"It's also the things I don't know"},{"time":302045,"text":"that have often brought me closer\nto everybody around me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306549,"text":"For eight straight Novembers, recently,"},{"time":308573,"text":"I traveled every year across Japan\nwith the Dalai Lama."},{"time":314001,"text":"And the one thing he said every day"},{"time":317125,"text":"that most seemed to give people\nreassurance and confidence"},{"time":320696,"text":"was, \"I don't know.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":324325,"text":"\"What's going to happen to Tibet?\""},{"time":327226,"text":"\"When are we ever\ngoing to get world peace?\""},{"time":330765,"text":"\"What's the best way to raise children?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":334134,"text":"\"Frankly,\" says this very wise man,"},{"time":337229,"text":"\"I don't know.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":340117,"text":"The Nobel Prize-winning\neconomist Daniel Kahneman"},{"time":343842,"text":"has spent more than 60 years now\nresearching human behavior,"},{"time":348369,"text":"and his conclusion is"},{"time":350425,"text":"that we are always much more confident\nof what we think we know"},{"time":355063,"text":"than we should be."},{"time":356812,"text":"We have, as he memorably puts it,"},{"time":359495,"text":"an \"unlimited ability\nto ignore our ignorance.\""},{"time":364849,"text":"We know -- quote, unquote -- our team\nis going to win this weekend,"},{"time":369960,"text":"and we only remember that knowledge"},{"time":372153,"text":"on the rare occasions when we're right."},{"time":375582,"text":"Most of the time, we're in the dark."},{"time":379319,"text":"And that's where real intimacy lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384580,"text":"Do you know what your lover\nis going to do tomorrow?"},{"time":388673,"text":"Do you want to know?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391621,"text":"The parents of us all,\nas some people call them,"},{"time":394458,"text":"Adam and Eve,"},{"time":395641,"text":"could never die, so long as they\nwere eating from the tree of life."},{"time":400631,"text":"But the minute they began nibbling"},{"time":402853,"text":"from the tree of the knowledge\nof good and evil,"},{"time":405459,"text":"they fell from their innocence."},{"time":407808,"text":"They grew embarrassed and fretful,"},{"time":410857,"text":"self-conscious."},{"time":412865,"text":"And they learned,\na little too late, perhaps,"},{"time":415257,"text":"that there are certainly some things\nthat we need to know,"},{"time":418021,"text":"but there are many, many more\nthat are better left unexplored."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423999,"text":"Now, when I was a kid,"},{"time":425948,"text":"I knew it all, of course."},{"time":429290,"text":"I had been spending 20 years\nin classrooms collecting facts,"},{"time":433526,"text":"and I was actually\nin the information business,"},{"time":436269,"text":"writing articles for Time Magazine."},{"time":439129,"text":"And I took my first real trip to Japan\nfor two-and-a-half weeks,"},{"time":444329,"text":"and I came back with a 40-page essay"},{"time":447633,"text":"explaining every last detail\nabout Japan's temples,"},{"time":451221,"text":"its fashions, its baseball games,"},{"time":454490,"text":"its soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457276,"text":"But underneath all that,"},{"time":459630,"text":"something that I couldn't understand"},{"time":462831,"text":"so moved me for reasons\nI couldn't explain to you yet,"},{"time":468087,"text":"that I decided to go and live in Japan."},{"time":472450,"text":"And now that I've been there for 28 years,"},{"time":475225,"text":"I really couldn't tell you\nvery much at all"},{"time":477649,"text":"about my adopted home."},{"time":480222,"text":"Which is wonderful,"},{"time":481593,"text":"because it means every day\nI'm making some new discovery,"},{"time":484497,"text":"and in the process,"},{"time":486012,"text":"looking around the corner\nand seeing the hundred thousand things"},{"time":489930,"text":"I'll never know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492964,"text":"Knowledge is a priceless gift."},{"time":496452,"text":"But the illusion of knowledge\ncan be more dangerous than ignorance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501895,"text":"Thinking that you know your lover"},{"time":505115,"text":"or your enemy"},{"time":506621,"text":"can be more treacherous"},{"time":508100,"text":"than acknowledging you'll never know them."},{"time":511937,"text":"Every morning in Japan, as the sun\nis flooding into our little apartment,"},{"time":516433,"text":"I take great pains not to consult\nthe weather forecast,"},{"time":520815,"text":"because if I do,"},{"time":522477,"text":"my mind will be overclouded, distracted,"},{"time":525764,"text":"even when the day is bright."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530160,"text":"I've been a full-time\nwriter now for 34 years."},{"time":534816,"text":"And the one thing that I have learned"},{"time":537720,"text":"is that transformation comes\nwhen I'm not in charge,"},{"time":541280,"text":"when I don't know what's coming next,"},{"time":543481,"text":"when I can't assume I am bigger\nthan everything around me."},{"time":549191,"text":"And the same is true in love"},{"time":551643,"text":"or in moments of crisis."},{"time":554929,"text":"Suddenly, we're back in that trishaw again"},{"time":558395,"text":"and we're bumping off the broad,\nwell-lit streets;"},{"time":562454,"text":"and we're reminded, really,\nof the first law of travel"},{"time":566142,"text":"and, therefore, of life:"},{"time":569090,"text":"you're only as strong\nas your readiness to surrender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575512,"text":"In the end, perhaps,"},{"time":577545,"text":"being human"},{"time":579262,"text":"is much more important"},{"time":581039,"text":"than being fully in the know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584763,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585973,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}